longBusinessSummary: Ossia International Limited, an investment holding company, imports, distributes, and retails apparel, sporting goods, footwear, bags, and accessories products primarily in Taiwan. The company also offers lifestyle, outdoors, and luggage products. It serves customers through a distribution network of outlets. The company was founded in 1982 and is based in Singapore.
